  "diagram_name": "Barrett & MacLean Zr vs Y Hydrothermal Alteration",
  "version": "1.0",
  "author": "Barrett, T.J. & MacLean, W.H.",
  "reference": {
    "citation": "Barrett, T.J. & MacLean, W.H. (1994). Chemostratigraphy and hydrothermal alteration in exploration for VHMS deposits in greenstones and younger volcanic rocks. In: Lentz, D.R. (ed.) Alteration and Alteration Processes Associated with Ore-Forming Systems. Geological Association of Canada Short Course Notes, 11, 433-467",
